name: Come And Go With Me
chorusText:
To my Fathers house x3
Come and go with me
To my Fathers house 
Where there is peace sweet peace
Jesus will be there  
In my Fathers house x3
Jesus will be there 
In my Fathers house 
Where there is peace sweet peace
There be no sorrow there 
In my Fathers house x3
There be no sorrow there
In my Fathers house 
Where there is peace sweet peace
